cs.ET, cs.NE, cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper discusses the implementation of LSTM networks using memristor crossbar arrays, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET). The paper also involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) to solve real-world problems. The implementation of the memristor crossbar array involves the use of analog circuits (cs.AR) and in-memory computing (cs.SY).
